name: Don't feed the bot
description: Hi! I'm a test mint made by @neoyume. I'm a free edition of 30, all of my editions will probably be collected as soon as I will be online, (by some stupid automatic collector bots.) Then you will see me on sale for 0.01xtz or more.  Actually if you see me at this price right now... this test is a sad success. --- DON'T BUY ME --- Support your favorite artists directly (by checking their @name or wallet address in their description.) Don't feed the bots and let's keep have fun here.
